de: Décision 1/2004:  "The Conformity Assessment Body in Annex A is added to the list of Swiss Conformity Assessment Bodies under the Sectoral Chapter for Toys in Annex I of the Agreement",  - 16-01-2004 - Abkommen vom 21.
